      </div>
      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-card-top"><div><div class="resource-name">NeetCode 75</div></div><div class="resource-icon" style="background:#faf5ff"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#7c3aed" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div></div>
        <div class="resource-desc">Best explained curated problems with video solutions for each question.</div>
        <a href="https://neetcode.io/practice" target="_blank" class="resource-link">Open <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section" style="animation-delay:0.15s">
    <div class="section-header"><span class="section-badge advanced">Advanced / Competitive</span><div class="section-line"></div></div>
    <div class="resource-grid">
      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-card-top"><div><div class="resource-name">Striver SDE Sheet</div></div><div class="resource-icon" style="background:#eff6ff"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></div></div>
        <div class="resource-desc">Deep interview preparation sheet covering all SDE interview topics in depth.</div>
        <a href="https://takeuforward.org/interviews/strivers-sde-sheet-top-coding-interview-problems/" target="_blank" class="resource-link">Open <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card">
